1)npm - node package manager 

node js core mein jo installed aata hai  wo kehlaata hain module 
npm se download krte hai wo hota hai package 

eg- text to speech 
google ke already kr rakha h 


2)Insalling adn uninstalling anyhting basics adn advanced 


install -> npm install  packageKaNaam 
uninstall -> npm uninstall packageKaNaam 



3)Version install bhi kr skte ho aap 

npm i accessibility@3.0.9




4)dependencies - packages and packages ki dependencies 
devdependencies - aise packages jo sirf development mei kaam aayege pr jab app ban jaayega aur upload ho jayega tb hum in packages ko use ni kr rhe honge 


  eg-  npm i nodemon --save-dev



5) kai baar aap koi script chlate ho aur usmei aap likhte ho ye command  
npm start 
npm run dev 
npm run concurrent 


npm ke sath agr run likga toh mtlb we have to find it in the script.. 

start test 



ab jaise tu package.json mei dund scrpit hogi 
waha start aur test vali script teri npm start ya npm test krke chlege.. 
